longBusinessSummary: Apotea AB (publ) operates an online pharmacy in Sweden. It offers products in the areas of allergy, face, child and parent, bite and sting, preparedness, animal, fever and aches, cold, home and household, aid, hair removal and shaving, hair care, hands and feet, intimate, dietary supplements, body care, stomach and intestine, food and beverage, mouth and teeth, toiletries, travel packaging and accessories, sex and lust, stop smoking, makeup, sun protection, wounds and injuries, sleep and sleep problems, training, weight control, vitamins and minerals, and eyes and ears. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
